三、教學目標 Objectives




This Reinforcement course will 
        help students obtain English language competency necessary for effective 
        communication. It will focus on consolidating reading and listening 
        skills and strategies.
        Students will be trained to apply appropriate reading strategies to 
        determine main ideas and supporting details, recognize basic patterns of 
        organization, draw conclusions, and understand vocabulary in context. 
        Upon completion of the course, students should be able to comprehend and 
        analyze college-level reading materials.
        Students will also be trained to deal with problems encountered when 
        listening to the target language. Upon completion of the course, they 
        will develop effective listening skills and strategies for everyday 
        conversation.




